PostMan RESTAPI Commands
Run the below commands in ur postman app to check the codes are working. Do let me know if there's an error :) 

Users
POST:
http://localhost:<your_localhostNo>/api/users
----create user ----
{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "role": "USER"
}

Accounts 
POST:
http://localhost:<your_localhostNo>/api/accounts
----Create Savings account----
{
  "user": {
    "userId": <USER_ID>   // replace with the actual userId generated
  },
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "balance": 1000
}

----Create Checking account----
{
  "user": {
    "userId": <USER_ID>   // replace with the actual userId generated
  },
  "accountType": "CHECKING",
  "balance": 500
}


Transactions
POST:
http://localhost:<your_localhostNo>/api/transactions
----Deposit----
{
  "accountId":  <Account_number>,    // The account you're depositing into
  "transactionType": "DEPOSIT",
  "amount": 200.0
}
----Withdrawal----
{
  "accountId": <Account_number>,    // The account you're withdrawing from
  "transactionType": "WITHDRAWAL",
  "amount": 50.0
}
----Transfer----
{
  "accountId": <Account_number,>    // Source account
  "transactionTo": <Account_number>, // Destination account
  "transactionType": "TRANSFER",
  "amount": 150.0
}
